		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message29040303">The aloofness of the girl reminds me of how some of my college friends are towards their parents. The distance widens and soon a rift forms. Growing up may be about doing your own thing and becoming and adult but you don't have to do it alone. I think that is what this is trying to say. I teared up a bit when her father was waiting near her apartment. Yeah, it was short and sweet with stellar animation.</div><div style="margin-top: 8px;"><em>Modified by Nagisa33, 03-02-14, 5:37 PM</em></div><div class="postActions"></div></td>
