		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message29133275">What I find really great about this short is that it is in fact an advertisement and the entire production of it was paid for as such - yet it is entirely able to communicate real feelings all the same. The first time I watched it, I didn't even know it was an advertisement, and I would have never guessed, either. A real show of the idea that art can be made from just about any base, commercial or not, dispelling the idea that something was never able to be strong simply because it was "made to make money".</div><div class="postActions"></div><div class="sig">&quot;My tables-meet it is I set it down<br />
